author: slava77
body:
This should clear the warnings appearing in comparisons since CMSSW_11_0_X_2019-07-17-2300.

wfs with the same numbers had 2023D\* in the names in the range [CMSSW_11_0_X_2019-07-10-2300, CMSSW_11_0_X_2019-07-17-2300). It seems OK to ignore this range of IBs and support just longer-lived name patterns for wfs ==> I'm renaming the existing entries instead of extending the map.
title: reco comparisons: rename 2023 to 2026 for phase-2 workflows in 110X
